SELECT
    CAST(MAX_SID AS BIGINT)               llave_tipo_contacto  ,
    CAST('axis' AS CHARACTER VARYING(30)) AS sistema_origen,
	CAST(cod_tipo_contacto AS BIGINT)               cod_tipo_contacto  ,
	CAST(descripcion_contacto AS CHARACTER VARYING(1000))   descripcion_contacto
	
FROM  
     
	(SELECT 1 as cod_tipo_contacto, 'Email' as descripcion_contacto
    UNION 
	SELECT 2 as cod_tipo_contacto, 'Celular' as descripcion_contacto
    UNION 
	SELECT 3 as cod_tipo_contacto, 'Telefono_fijo' as descripcion_contacto
	UNION 
	SELECT 4 as cod_tipo_contacto, 'Fono_indeterminado' as descripcion_contacto
    ) 
LEFT JOIN
    (   SELECT
            MAX(llave_tipo_contacto) AS MAX_SID
        FROM
            data_clientes_cl.cdm_cl_dim_Tipo_contacto_t ) LKP
ON
    1 = 1
